  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nLodestar blocks include attestations voted for orphaned head, for example https://altair-devnet-2-explorer.ethdevops.io/block/351#attestations and https://altair-devnet-2-explorer.ethdevops.io/block/407#attestations\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nWe should only include attestations with correct source, target and head.\r\n\r\n**Steps to Reproduce**\r\n\r\nJoin `altair-devnet-2`",
